## 📁 Project Structure

```
Card Catalog POS/
├── checkoutdesignator/          # Backend Python package
│   ├── app/main.py              # FastAPI application entry point
│   ├── routers/                 # API endpoints
│   │   ├── customers.py         # Customer management
│   │   ├── inventory.py         # Inventory operations
│   │   ├── orders.py            # Order processing
│   │   ├── preorders.py         # Pre-order system
│   │   ├── users.py             # Staff user management
│   │   ├── checklist.py         # Daily checklist system
│   │   └── backup.py            # Database export endpoints
│   ├── services/                # Business logic layer
│   ├── models.py                # Database models
│   ├── schemas.py               # API request/response models
│   ├── auth.py                  # JWT authentication
│   ├── database.py              # Database connection
│   └── cli.py                   # Command-line interface
│
├── frontend/                    # React frontend
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── pages/               # Main application pages
│   │   ├── components/          # Reusable UI components
│   │   ├── api/                 # API client functions
│   │   ├── hooks/               # React Query hooks
│   │   └── contexts/            # React contexts (auth, etc.)
│   └── package.json
│
├── scripts/                     # Utility scripts
│   ├── seed_staff.py            # Create staff accounts
│   ├── seed_default_customer.py # Create default customer
│   ├── seed_singles_item.py     # Create "Singles" item
│   ├── backup_database.sh       # Database backup script
│   └── migrate_*.py             # Database migrations
│
├── docs/                        # Documentation
│   ├── SETUP.md                 # 📖 Complete setup guide
│   ├── DATABASE_BACKUP.md       # Backup documentation
│   └── ...                      # Other guides
│
├── tests/                       # Automated tests
├── db_backups/                  # Automatic backup storage
├── checkoutdesignator.db        # SQLite database (created on init)
├── start.sh                     # Start script for both servers
├── pyproject.toml               # Python dependencies
└── README.md                    # This file
```

